,428],"tutor_black-2-white-2":[173,180,196,214,231,272,276,277,282,289,340,399,428,492],"tutor_omega-ruby-alpha-sapphire":[173,180,196,231,272,276,277,282,289,340,351,352,428,492],"tutor_ultra-sun-ultra-moon":[173,180,196,231,272,276,277,282,289,340,351,352,428,492,673,675]},"species":"absol","gen":"generation-iii","leg":false,"myth":false,"baby":false,"eggs":["ground"],"flavor":[{"version":"ruby","text":"Every time ABSOL appears before people, it is followed by a disaster such as an earthquake or a tidal wave. As a result, it came to be known as the disaster POK\u00e9MON."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"ABSOL has the ability to foretell the coming of natural disasters. It lives in a harsh, rugged mountain environment. This POK\u00e9MON very rarely ventures down from the mountains."},{"version":"emerald","text":"It sharply senses even subtle changes in the sky and the land to predict natural disasters. It is a long-lived POK\u00e9MON that has a life-span of 100 years."},{"version":"firered","text":"It appears when it senses an impending natural disaster. As a result, it was mistaken as a doom-bringer."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"It appears when it senses an impending natural disaster. As a result, it was mistaken as a doom-bringer."},{"version":"diamond","text":"It senses coming disasters and appears before people only to warn them of impending danger."},{"version":"pearl","text":"It senses coming disasters and appears before people only to warn them of impending danger."},{"version":"platinum","text":"Rumored to sense disasters with its horn, it became a target. It fled deep into the mountains."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"It has the ability to foretell natural disasters. Its life span is over a hundred years."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"It has the ability to foretell natural disasters. Its life span is over a hundred years."},{"version":"black","text":"Rumored to sense disasters with its horn, it became a target. It fled deep into the mountains."},{"version":"white","text":"Rumored to sense disasters with its horn, it became a target. It fled deep into the mountains."},{"version":"black-2","text":"It appears from deep in the mountains to warn people about upcoming disasters it has sensed with its horn."},{"version":"white-2","text":"It appears from deep in the mountains to warn people about upcoming disasters it has sensed with its horn."},{"version":"x","text":"It senses coming disasters and appears before people only to warn them of impending danger."},{"version":"y","text":"It appears when it senses an impending natural disaster. As a result, it was mistaken as a doom bringer."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Every time Absol appears before people, it is followed by a disaster such as an earthquake or a tidal wave. As a result, it came to be known as the disaster Pok\u00e9mon."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Absol has the ability to foretell the coming of natural disasters. It lives in a harsh, rugged mountain environment. This Pok\u00e9mon very rarely ventures down from the mountains."},{"version":"sun","text":"Long ago, superstitions were spread about it, saying it brought disaster. This fed a hatred of it, and it was driven deep into the mountains."},{"version":"moon","text":"Although it\u2019s said to bring disaster, in actuality, this Pok\u00e9mon possesses a calm disposition and warns people of any crises that loom."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"The only thing unlucky about Absol is its appearance. It protects fields and warns people of disaster, so one ought to be grateful for it."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"The elderly call it the disaster Pok\u00e9mon and detest it, but interest in its power to predict disasters is on the rise."},{"version":"sword","text":"Swift as the wind, Absol races through fields and mountains. Its curved, bow-like horn is acutely sensitive to the warning signs of natural disasters."},{"version":"shield","text":"Because of this Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s ability to detect danger, people mistook Absol as a bringer of doom."}],"evo":{"name":"absol","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/359.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/shiny/359.png","capture":30,"happiness":35,"growth":"medium-slow","gender":4,"hatch":25,"ev":{"attack":2},"forms":[{"id":10057,"name":"absol-mega","sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/10057.png"},{"id":10307,"name":"absol-mega-z","sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/10307.png"}]}